  "instructions": [
    "Preheat a yakimono grill or grill pan to medium-high heat.",
    "Cut the courgettes into 1/2-inch thick slices and season with salt and black pepper.",
    "Grill the courgettes for 3-4 minutes per side, or until tender and slightly charred.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together the Mongolian chili paste, soy sauce, rice vinegar, hoisin sauce, and cornstarch.",
    "Add the whisked sauce to the grilled courgettes and toss to coat.",
    "Split the bao buns in half and toast until lightly browned.",
    "Fill each bao bun with a few slices of the courgette mixture, some chopped scallions, and a sprinkle of toasted sesame seeds.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
  ],
